cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper focuses on generating personalized explanations for recommendations using natural language processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves recommender systems, which suggests the sub-categories cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses deep neural networks, which falls under the sub-category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves cross-domain experiments, which suggests the sub-category cs.CY (Computers and Society).
